#: ../../docs/classes/class_collisionshape.rst:19
msgid ""
"Editor facility for creating and editing collision shapes in 3D space. "
"You can use this node to represent all sorts of collision shapes, for "
"example, add this to an :ref:`Area <class_Area>` to give it a detection "
"shape, or add it to a :ref:`PhysicsBody <class_PhysicsBody>` to create a "
"solid object. **IMPORTANT**: this is an Editor-only helper to create "
"shapes, use :ref:`CollisionObject.shape_owner_get_shape "
"<class_CollisionObject_method_shape_owner_get_shape>` to get the actual "
"shape."
msgstr ""

